sness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40002,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/11\/way-of-allah-multiplied\/","url_meta":{"origin":24126,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Spending in the way of Allah multiplied","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Khuraym ibn Fatik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever donates charity in the way of Allah, it will be multiplied up to seven hundred times in his record.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1625 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u062e\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32125,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/cheerful-face-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24126,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Cheerful face, guiding travelers are charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSmiling in the face of your brother is your charity. Enjoining good and forbidding evil is charity. Guiding a lost man through the land is your charity. Lending your eyesight to a man who cannot see\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img